metadata.name: Detroit
metadata.description:
detroit. 
most call it a comeback story. 
a rise from the ashes. 
but those who live it. 
generations who've built it. 
never left.

Digital: 4,463 px. x 6,765 px .  
Physical: acrylic and spray paint on wood panel. 
24" x 36" x 1 3/8"

*Proof of physical ownership. 
 Owner of this NFT also owns the Physical painting created by Wetiko.  
If the new owner wishes not to handle the physical, Wetiko will store safely.  
When transferring this NFT, owner must be responsible for safely packaging and shipping to either the new owner, or back to Wetiko for safe storage.  
None of the physical ties are on-chain. It's more a non-binding agreement Wetiko has with his collectors.  
Any questions: kyle@wetiko.work
